Live preview: <a href="themesbymariaays1.tumblr.com">themesbymariaays1.tumblr.com</a>


Customizations: 

  Primary and secondar colours can be changed in the theme options.

    Primary Colour: sidebar borders, title link colour, ask/submit link background colour, pagination link colour, permalink colour, tags background colour
    Secondary Colour: link hover colour (title, tags, permalink), ask/submit link hover background colour
  
  Background and sidebar images can also be changed in the theme options.
